sequenceDiagram
    participant BUYER as Buyer
    participant BD as Buyer's Dealer
    participant PLAT as Trading Platform
    participant SD as Seller's Dealer
    participant SELLER as Seller
    participant TRACE as TRACE / RTRS
    participant FICC as FICC / NSCC
    participant FW as Fedwire / DTC
    participant BCUST as Buyer's Custodian
    participant SCUST as Seller's Custodian

    Note over BUYER,SCUST: T+0: TRADE DAY

    BUYER->>PLAT: RFQ for $5M face UST 10Y
    PLAT->>SD: Broadcast RFQ to dealers
    SD->>PLAT: Quote: Bid 98.25 / Ask 98.31
    BUYER->>PLAT: Lift offer at 98.31
    PLAT->>BD: Trade confirmed (buy side)
    PLAT->>SD: Trade confirmed (sell side)
    PLAT->>TRACE: Report trade within 15 min

    Note over BUYER,SCUST: T+0: POST-TRADE PROCESSING

    BD->>FICC: Submit trade details
    SD->>FICC: Submit trade details
    FICC->>FICC: Match and validate<br/>Calculate net obligations<br/>Novate (become counterparty)

    Note over BUYER,SCUST: T+1: SETTLEMENT DAY

    FICC->>FW: DVP instructions
    FW->>SCUST: Debit securities from seller
    FW->>BCUST: Credit securities to buyer
    FW->>SCUST: Credit cash to seller
    FW->>BCUST: Debit cash from buyer

    BCUST->>BUYER: Confirm settlement
    SCUST->>SELLER: Confirm settlement

    Note over BUYER,SCUST: Settlement complete - DVP eliminates counterparty risk
